item.title: [PI] hp counter help
item.dc:creator: @Runecessor Runecessor
item.description:
@Runecessor wrote:

Usually if you did a skill command in which sets your skills to 99 upon the entering of the command it will do that so try to log out and then log back into the client. But if that as already been attempted then you need to either look at the command or reset the maximum level for your HP display. My assumption is that someone was using a few servers to peice together and you got the short end of the stick because this is clearly not an original piece of work.
